'''哈爾科夫人民共和國'''（{{lang-ru|Харьковская Народная Республика}}）是一個由[[小绿人_(俄乌战争)|侵入乌克兰的俄国无识别标识武裝分子]]建立的伪「國家」。这些俄国武裝分子占領哈尔科夫地方行政大樓後，於2014年4月7日在大樓大廳宣告獨立<ref name="KRR1"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.liveleak.com/view?i=9bd_1396967425 |title=Declaration of Kharkiv People's Republic |accessdate=2014-04-12 |archive-date=2015-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408202650/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26910210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月8日，烏克蘭官方奪回該大樓，將叛亂勢力掃除至外，估計有七十名武裝分子被逮捕<ref name=KRR2>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kharkiv-settles-down-while-pro-russian-separatists-still-hold-buildings-in-luhansk-donetsk-342517.html |title=Kharkiv settles down, while pro-Russian separatists still hold buildings in Luhansk, Donetsk |accessdate=2014-04-12 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412140528/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kharkiv-settles-down-while-pro-russian-separatists-still-hold-buildings-in-luhansk-donetsk-342517.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/media/video/kharkiv-separatists-declare-republic/25325304.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-12 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412072016/http://www.rferl.org/media/video/kharkiv-separatists-declare-republic/25325304.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

根據相關人士說法，他們計畫基於國際法下與他國建立關係<ref name=KRR1/><ref name=KRR2/>，並在該州進行公投確認所謂“主權獨立”<ref name="KRR1" />。同時尋求以逃離祖國尋求俄羅斯庇護的前[[烏克蘭總統|烏克蘭總統]][[維克多·亞努科維奇|維克多·亞努科維奇]]的名義將政權合法化<ref name="KRR1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.focus-fen.net/news/2014/04/07/332351/pro-russia-activists-declare-establishment-of-kharkiv-peoples-republic.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-12 |archive-date=2014-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409121553/http://www.focus-fen.net/news/2014/04/07/332351/pro-russia-activists-declare-establishment-of-kharkiv-peoples-republic.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

11月22日，別茲柳多夫卡附近的一個火車站遭遇爆炸襲擊。這是兩周以來哈爾科夫發生的第三次爆炸。<ref name="kharkiv news">{{cite news |url=http://kh.vgorode.ua/news/sobytyia/243191-smy-v-kharkove-vzorvalas-tsysterna-v-zheleznodorozhnom-depo |title=На ж/д станции "Основа" взорвалась цистерна |trans-title=一列油罐车于"Osnova"火车站被炸 |language=ru |newspaper=vgorode.ua |date=22 November 2014 |accessdate=23 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225212549/http://kh.vgorode.ua/news/sobytyia/243191-smy-v-kharkove-vzorvalas-tsysterna-v-zheleznodorozhnom-depo |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://lenta.ru/news/2014/11/22/kharkov/ |title=В Харькове подорвали железнодорожную цистерну |trans-title=在哈爾科夫，一列儲油罐車被炸毀 |language=ru |newspaper=Lenta.ru |date=22 November 2014 |accessdate=23 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123062514/http://lenta.ru/news/2014/11/22/kharkov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在11月9日哈爾科夫市中心發生的爆炸曾經炸傷13人。<ref name="kharkiv news"></ref>另有報道稱在哈爾科夫火車站發現了數包爆炸物和彈藥。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.liga.net/news/politics/4160726-v_kharkove_na_vokzale_vyyavili_sumki_so_vzryvchatkoy_i_patronami.htm |title=В Харькове на вокзале выявили сумки со взрывчаткой и патронами |trans-title=哈爾科夫火車站發現多包爆炸品和彈藥 |language=ru |newspaper=Liga.Novosty |date=22 November 2014 |accessdate=23 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141125134325/http://news.liga.net/news/politics/4160726-v_kharkove_na_vokzale_vyyavili_sumki_so_vzryvchatkoy_i_patronami.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>據哈爾科夫檢察官透露，有九名“哈爾科夫游擊隊”成員被指控與12起爆炸案相關，並已遭拘禁。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.liga.net/news/politics/4136386-na_schetu_zaderzhannykh_kharkovskikh_partizan_12_teraktov.htm |title=На счету задержанных "Харьковских партизан" – 12 терактов |trans-title=起訴被拘禁的“哈爾科夫游擊隊”成員-12次恐怖襲擊 |language=ru |newspaper=Liga.Novosty |date=22 November 2014 |accessdate=23 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141124045022/http://news.liga.net/news/politics/4136386-na_schetu_zaderzhannykh_kharkovskikh_partizan_12_teraktov.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

